wnload PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5754633\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5754633\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lhc1704371292385.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lhc1704371292385.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lhc1704371292385.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tzw1665702711695\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Working with Modeled Properties \n      \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__working_with_modeled_properties_35849\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create modeled properties using editors available on the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More\n         Editors</span> menu. Use a modeled property by clicking the More icon (<img alt=\"icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__image_bcc_1jl_zzb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/ellipsis.png?_LANG=enus\"/>) in the appropriate property of an entity or field. </p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4724e1_d4725e1_d4726e1\">To create a modeled property:\n <ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4727e1_d4728e1_d4729e1\">In the Uniface IDE, click the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More Editors</span> and choose the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Modeled</span> property. One of:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4730e1_d4731e1_d4732e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Entity Interface</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4733e1_d4734e1_d4735e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Interface</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4736e1_d4737e1_d4738e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Syntax</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4739e1_d4740e1_d4741e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Layout</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1\">Enter a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Name</span> and optional\n                     <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Description</span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4745e1_d4746e1_d4747e1\">Set the other properties, as appropriate.\n <p class=\"p\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__p_d10346e1_d10347e1_d10348e1\">For information about the properties, press F1 to display the online help.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4748e1_d4749e1_d4750e1\">To save the modeled property, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt;Save</span></span>. <p class=\"p\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__p_d10349e1_d10350e1_d10351e1\">Alternatively, click\n                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">OK</span> to save it and exit the editor.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__p_d10352e1_d10353e1_d10354e1\">Modeled properties are implicitly defined in an untyped library called <code class=\"ph codeph\">LIB</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4751e1_d4752e1_d4753e1\">To use a modeled property, when editing an entity or field:\n <ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4754e1_d4755e1_d4756e1\">In the Properties Inspector, click the More icon\n                     (<img alt=\"icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__image_rkg_fjl_zzb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/ellipsis.png?_LANG=enus\"/>) of the relevant property: <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4757e1_d4758e1_d4759e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database Interface</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4760e1_d4761e1_d4762e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Syntax</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4763e1_d4764e1_d4765e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Layout</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__li_d4766e1_d4767e1_d4768e1\">Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Use modeled</span> to browse and select the modeled property you want to use.\n </li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tzw1665702711695__p_d10355e1_d10356e1_d10357e1\">The property now references a modeled property. If the modeled property changes and the entity or component is recompiled, it will inherit the modified modeled property.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hzd1665702710226.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Modeled Entity Interface</a><p>A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzg1665702711012.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Modeled Field Interface</a><p>A Modeled Field Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijx1665702711766.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Modeled Field Layout</a><p>A Modeled Field Layout is a Development Object that defines the way data is displayed.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbr1665702712405.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Modeled Field Syntax</a><p>A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5754633\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5754633\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Working with Modeled Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Working with Modeled Properties Create modeled properties using editors available on the More Editors menu. Use a modeled property by clicking the More icon ( ) in the appropriate property of an entity or field. To create a modeled property: In the Uniface IDE, click the More Editors and choose the Modeled property. One of: Entity Interface Field Interface Field Syntax Field Layout Enter a Name and optional Description . Set the other properties, as appropriate. For information about the properties, press F1 to display the online help. To save the modeled property, choose File >Save . Alternatively, click OK to save it and exit the editor. Modeled properties are implicitly defined in an untyped library called LIB . To use a modeled property, when editing an entity or field: In the Properties Inspector, click the More icon ( ) of the relevant property: Database Interface Field Syntax Field Layout Click Use modeled to browse and select the modeled property you want to use. The property now references a modeled property. If the modeled property changes and the entity or component is recompiled, it will inherit the modified modeled property. Related Links Modeled Entity Interface A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity. Modeled Field Interface A Modeled Field Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Field. Modeled Field Layout A Modeled Field Layout is a Development Object that defines the way data is displayed. Modeled Field Syntax A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}